tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE respondent_demographics (
    respondent_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    location VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE respondent_demographics (
    respondent_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    respondent_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender CHAR(1),
    location VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    respondent_id INT,
    survey_question VARCHAR(255),
    response_text VARCHAR(255),
    response_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Respondents (
  respondent_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  respondent_name VARCHAR(50),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  profession VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Responses (
  response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  respondent_id INT,
  survey_id INT,
  response_value TEXT,
  response_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE respondents (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  first_name VARCHAR(50),
  last_name VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(100),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE surveys (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(100),
  description TEXT,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE responses (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  respondent_id INT,
  survey_id INT,
  response TEXT,
  response_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE demographics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  respondent_id INT,
  location VARCHAR(100),
  income DECIMAL,
  education_level VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE respondent_demographics (
    respondent_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR,
    location VARCHAR,
    income DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    respondent_id INT REFERENCES respondent_demographics(respondent_id),
    survey_id INT,
    question1 VARCHAR,
    question2 VARCHAR,
    answer1 VARCHAR,
    answer2 VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE survey_targets (
    target_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    target_name VARCHAR,
    criteria VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE survey_campaigns (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    target_id INT REFERENCES survey_targets(target_id)
)

CREATE TABLE survey_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    response_id INT REFERENCES survey_responses(response_id),
    campaign_id INT REFERENCES survey_campaigns(campaign_id),
    result VARCHAR
)
